Prepares an intent for a DemoActivity.

Parameters:
intent - the intent to be used to launch the sublcass of DemoActivity.
demoActivityId - the id that will be used to store the information about the 'never show again' checkbox.
listPoints - an ArrayList of LabeledPoint to Display.

isNeverShowAgain

public static boolean isNeverShowAgain(android.app.Activity caller,
                                       String demoActivityId)
Allows to check if a demo activity has been set never to display again.

Parameters:
caller - the activity that is calling the DemoActivity. Its SharedPreferences will be used internally by the DemoActivity.
demoActivityId - the id that will be used to store the information about the 'never show again' checkbox.
